FoxRabbit
Class Fox

java.lang.Object
  FoxRabbit.Animal
      FoxRabbit.Fox

public class Fox
extends Animal

Fox class represents the logic provided by the fox to search and traverse the rabbit over the board. The class has different strategies for traversing the board and locating the rabbit location. It also has the logic to inform other foxes about the rabbit location to provide full attack on the rabbit when seen
